'''''The Burial of Kojo''''' ni filime yikinamico yo muri [[Gana]] 2018 yanditswe, yahimbwe kandi iyobowe na Blitz Bazawule<ref>“The Burial of Kojo,” Reviewed: A Boldly Lyrical Portrait of a ... <nowiki>https://www.newyorker.com</nowiki> › Culture › Films</ref> . Yakozwe na Bazawule, Ama K. Abebrese na Kwaku Obeng Boateng,   yafatiwe amashusho yose muri [[Gana]] ku ngengo yimari iciriritse, hamwe nabakozi baho ndetse nabakinnyi benshi ba mbere<ref>'The Burial of Kojo' Review - Variety <nowiki>https://variety.com</nowiki> › film › reviews › the-burial-of-kojo-r...</ref>.  Iyi filime ivuga amateka ya Kojo, usigaye apfira mu kirombe cya zahabu cyatawe, mu gihe umukobwa we muto Esi yagendaga mu gihugu cy'umwuka kugira ngo amukize<ref>'The Burial of Kojo' Review: A Dazzling Modern Fable - The New <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 2019/03/28 › movies › the-bu...</ref>.

Yerekanwe bwa mbere ku isi i New York ku ya 21 Nzeri 2018, mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi rya Urban World<ref>Streaming: The Burial of Kojo; Fugue – a magical double bill <nowiki>https://www.theguardian.com</nowiki> › film › apr › the-burial-of-...</ref>,   aho ryamenyekanye nk'Imvugo Nziza (Sinema y'Isi).  Iyi filime yakiriye ibihembo icyenda mu bihembo bya 15 bya Afurika Movie Academy Awards kandi yatsindiye bibiri, harimo Filime Nziza Yambere Yakozwe n'Umuyobozi<ref>THE BURIAL OF KOJO - Array Now <nowiki>http://www.arraynow.com</nowiki> › the-burial-of-kojo</ref>.  CYatanzwe na ARRAY kandi yasohotse kuri serivise ya Netflix ku ya 31 Werurwe 2019,   ibaye filime ya mbere yo muri [[Gana]] yerekanwe bwa mbere mu bihugu byatoranijwe ku isi, kuri Netflix<ref>'The Burial of Kojo' Depicts The Beauty of Ghanaian Culture ... <nowiki>https://shadowandact.com</nowiki> › the-burial-of-kojo-depicts-t...</ref>.   

